title: "ipis-thesis-pyrolysis-epr: chance-constrained design of decentralized plastic-pyrolysis networks under feedstock-composition uncertainty"
abstract: "Reproducibility archive: validated pyrolysis yield and flowsheet models, feedstock-composition uncertainty set, Gaussian-process surrogate, two-stage stochastic and chance-constrained superstructure optimization, SAA replication study, techno-economic analysis with Sobol sensitivity, and single-script regeneration of all manuscript figures."
